{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b9559c4c6a","title":"中央关于加强公共食堂领导的批语","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ffdfad0771","index":0,"year":1960,"month":3,"day":15,"articleId":"b9559c4c6a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2343d518c6","type":"title","text":"中央关于加强公共食堂领导的批语毛泽东（一九六O年三月十五日）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"794c0e7d51","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"fc3d452ae0","type":"appellation","text":"上海局，各协作区委员会，各省委、市委、区党委，中央一级各部委、各党组：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"c2468dfdbe","type":"paragraph","text":"《八个省农村公共食堂情况》一件，《河南省农村公共食堂情况》一件，《一九五九年年底全国农村公共食堂情况》一件，都好，使人看了高兴。现在发给你们研究、参考、仿行。其中放在括号内的一些指示性的断语，是中央加上去的。请你们对这个极端重要的公共食堂问题，在今年一年内，认真大抓两次，上半年一次，下半年一次，学贵州、河南等省那样作出科学的总结，普遍推行。从省到社四级都应组织生活福利委员会，派一个懂得政治、热心肯干、善于分析问题、勤于到食堂考察研究而没有一点官僚主义作风的书记去充当领导。在每一个食堂内都组织一个食堂管理委员会。工厂、矿山、街道、机关、学校、团体、军队的公共食堂，一律照此办理。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"bb074217cc","type":"paragraph","text":" 中　　央一九六O年三月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"f3a6fdf2e9","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"caf826b4b7","type":"paragraph","text":"（......就全国说来，能够争取占全体农村人口百分之八十的人到食堂吃饭，就很好了。像河南、湖南、四川、云南、贵州、上海、安徽七个省市争取了百分之九十以上的人到食堂吃饭，当然更好。但其他各省、市、区，暂时达不到这个程度的也不要勉强，两三年内争取逐渐达到，是可以的）......。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"63afb7d4a7","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"24c222bcde","type":"paragraph","text":"这个办法极好，应当普遍推行。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"299402e40d","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"f8861a236b","type":"paragraph","text":"这个民主制度，各地都应建立起来。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"7d43d588c0","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"4bd0bf9398","type":"paragraph","text":"中央认为，这个问题，必须坚决地逐步地实行解决，一律按照河南、湖南、四川、云南、贵州、上海、安徽七省市的办法去做为好。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"4d10e6116d","type":"subtitle","text":"六","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"0898c4dcf1","type":"paragraph","text":"他们应当研究，提出意见。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"5073e65478","type":"subtitle","text":"七","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"b4cd316be4","type":"paragraph","text":"用植物秸、杆、根、叶大制淀粉，是一项大发明，全国一切公社，都应推行。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"c8cd35ba5c","type":"subtitle","text":"八","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"649d1e93f8","type":"paragraph","text":"各地应当积极研究。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"49a6409c80","type":"subtitle","text":"九","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"d33febad50","type":"paragraph","text":"请各省、市、区党委注意，从省到社，一律建立生活福利委员会，而以办好食堂为重点任务。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"bc7f2398df","type":"subtitle","text":"十","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"1c6e958758","type":"paragraph","text":"中央认为，这些办法极好。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"d5735fcf82","type":"subtitle","text":"十一","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"bac3c6f6b1","type":"paragraph","text":"中央认为，以上各项制度和办法，都很好。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"bed5191d28","type":"subtitle","text":"十二","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"da2bd07faf","type":"paragraph","text":"中央认为，以上各项缺点，都应迅速改正，变三类食堂为一类食堂。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"8b17652287","type":"subtitle","text":"十三","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"},{"id":"dcfdc416f5","type":"paragraph","text":"中央认为，这样的统计极为有益，使读者对全国面貌，一目了然。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a"}],"page":{"id":"ed852e543d","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b9559c4c6a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}